                            <comment id="16999500" author="marett" created="Wed, 18 Dec 2019 20:43:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=kwin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;kwin&quot;&gt;kwin&lt;/a&gt; I won&apos;t have the bandwidth to focus on this and would also need to debug it. What may help is to build a failing test. This test may be similar to those added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCRVLT-304&quot; title=&quot;Add tests that cover combinations of node and property filters&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JCRVLT-304&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;JCRVLT-304&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
