&lt;p&gt;Update: The problem is &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/blob/f234d92e51bfd29fa1437120008d945ec7b8e33b/vault-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/vault/fs/impl/io/DocViewSAXImporter.java#L969&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/blob/f234d92e51bfd29fa1437120008d945ec7b8e33b/vault-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/vault/fs/impl/io/DocViewSAXImporter.java#L969&lt;/a&gt; which will still remove properties not contained in the package (although they should be excluded)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
